            <title>[PDFBOX-2357] PDTrueTypeFont has no method to load font from stream</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2357</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The PDTrueTypeFont had formely static method to load a font from a stream. Now that method is gone. As far as I can see without a reason. Probably removed by mistake.&lt;/p&gt;

